# Playwright visual-regression baselines.
# Previously-tracked baselines were generated against the old design and are
# no longer meaningful — regenerate from a single canonical environment
# (Linux CI) once the visual surface stabilises, then drop this line if we
# decide to commit them again.
**/*.spec.ts-snapshots/

# Local ad-hoc screenshot scratch directory at the repo root — not
# referenced by any tool, ignored so manual captures don't pollute the index.
/screenshots/

